      {"@type":"Question","name":"What is the PESCO reference number format?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The PESCO reference number is always 14 digits. No letters, no dashes. Example: 01234567890123. It stays the same every month and is used for all online payments and bill checking."}},
